OL,3,CSocial club in Swansea teetering on
OL,4,Cedge of sinkhole to be knocked down
OL,6,FA social club in Swansea that has been
OL,7,Fteetering on the edge of a sinkhole
OL,8,Ffor more than two years is to be
OL,9,Fknocked down.
OL,11,FCwmfelin Social Club closed its doors
OL,12,Fin August 2023 after a sinkhole
OL,13,Fappeared in the club's car park,
OL,14,Fforcing 600 members and 20 employees
OL,15,Fto leave the building.
OL,17,FThe sinkhole is said to have been
OL,18,Fcaused by a collapsed culvert 10
OL,19,Fmetres under the club and the remains
OL,20,Fof a tramline.
