OL,3,CSocial club in Swansea teetering on
OL,4,Cedge of sinkhole to be knocked down
OL,6,FNow, the decision has been made to
OL,7,Fdemolish the building, after more than
OL,8,Ftwo years of working to find a
OL,9,Fresolution between the members of the
OL,10,Fclub, Welsh Water and Network Rail.
OL,12,FIt was initially hoped that the club
OL,13,Fwould be closed for a few weeks while
OL,14,Fsafety work was carried out, however
OL,15,Fthe sinkhole has posed particular
OL,16,Fchallenges as it is on private land
OL,17,Fand close to existing buildings.
OL,19,FClub chairman Mike Kennedy told ITV
OL,20,FCymru Wales: "It's taken such a long
OL,21,Ftime to come to this decision.
