OL,6,F"It has taken that time because we
OL,7,Fwere trying to find other ways to
OL,8,Frepair the club without taking it
OL,9,Fdown, but unfortunately that's the
OL,10,Fonly way to get access. Yeah, I am
OL,11,Freally disappointed."
OL,13,FIt is not yet known whether the club
OL,14,Fwill be rebuilt.
